dc_title_s: Cultural Features, Areas: Prince George's County, Maryland, 2009
dc_description_s: This dataset contains smokestack/cooling towers, cemeteries, pools, pads, tanks, and tracks within Prince George's County. Smokestacks/cooling towers include the attribute of height in feet. Pads are attributed with pad type, including patio, athletic, helipad, concrete, and asphalt. This data was captured for use in general mapping at a scale of 1:1200.
dc_creator_sm: The Maryland-National Capital Park & Planning Commission
